Ship - Class in portsim.ship
Represents a ship whose movement is managed by the system.
Ship(long, String, String, NauticalFlag) - Constructor for class Ship
Creates a new ship with the given IMO number, name, origin port flag and nautical flag.
shipArrives(Ship) - Method in class Quay
Docks the given ship at the Quay so that the quay becomes occupied.
shipDeparts() - Method in class Quay
Removes the current ship docked at the quay.
ShipMovement - Class in portsim.movement
The movement of a ship coming into or out of the port.
ShipMovement(long, MovementDirection, Ship) - Constructor for class ShipMovement
Creates a new ship movement with the given action time and direction to be undertaken with the given ship.
